::GoldenEye::

She flies over the battle field and watches the goings on.  She sees 
the Predacons and the Allience team up and try to arradicate the 
Maximals and their base.  She soars high up in the air currents and 
observes the battle.  She knows she was build as a Predacon.  But 
until now, she was still deciding where she should go and who she 
should join.  She knew that in order to survive, she would have to 
pick the strongest group.  And the Maximals were not it.  They were 
getting destroyed down there.  She felt a little sorry for them.  
They were a brave group of bots, willing to die for what they 
beleived in.  Unfortunately, that's just what they were doing, dying.
She stayed in the upper air currents and just circled above the 
ship.
